{"tid":1397732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發！] 有自稱記者喺遮打集會起公務員底！","createTime":"2019-08-02T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:14:33.000Z","uid":273098,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10179866e558e6cf9036370c30c16ec9fbbb5994","tid":1397732,"uid":273098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"代女性朋友post<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n朋友不是公務員<br />\n<br />\n剛剛喺遮打<br />\n有個著住間條衫自稱係星島既記者拎電話做網上問卷<br />\n<br />\n朋友應承左 想睇下佢問乜<br />\n<br />\n全份問卷有三條<br />\n內容大約如下<br />\n<br />\n第一條<br />\n請問你是<br />\n1)現職公務員<br />\n2)退休公務員<br />\n<br />\n第二條<br />\n請提供你的<br />\n1)部門<br />\n2)職級<br />\n<br />\n第三條<br />\n你是否讚成以下6項訴求<br />\n1-5 5大訴求<br />\n6 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n朋友亂咁答左<br />\n又醒唔起要追問佢有冇記者証就比條友走左<br />\n<br />\n不過愈諗愈唔妥<br />\n會唔會係不明仕想起公務員底呢！<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足遇到類似情況？<br />\n我地係咪應該向星島查詢當日有冇派記者做問卷？"},{"pid":"49070a67d25e7b41a78dcefce72d5dbb3829d59c","tid":1397732,"uid":273098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76ed1d35795588226f9f8f067769455cbc00a8fb","tid":1397732,"uid":273098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86ed2bab97f040ad6005c98e4133d63157612b09","tid":1397732,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"8月5日朝早不如去中環金鐘逐間逐戶探望仲要番工既朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0f736a8df6d3e938f54451dadc67d7efaf6be18","tid":1397732,"uid":185652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"當公務員係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩<br />\n邊會答第二條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8